{
  "stem": "6845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the only possession for the rest of the year, this purple metal bowl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they gave us some-- they filled us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, now, eat it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't see how to arrange it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I tasted it, and I thought, I'll die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I figured I won't die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I have to find another solution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember, I sat down in a-- kind of in a quieter place somehow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a dress on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I pulled the dress up, put my legs kind of apart, and kind of tried to camouflage it with the two hands-- I was scraping a hole in the ground, in a very dry, dry ground.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's what I tried to accomplish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they say, if they catch you, you do something with the food, they shot you on the place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know why that I wasn't yet ready to die that-- when they said it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But meantime, the fact was that I tried to pour that soup kind of underneath myself and between my legs to camouflage it in the ground.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, some of the soup went there, but all of it didn't go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly-- I could hardly wait to get up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I don't even know when I started to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I know I couldn't eat that first soup, the first dinner, first supper, or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we were-- then I started right away to look at more pathetic people than I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I saw a girlfriend, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's one of the ones with the nylon stockings bet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she was dead in a corner, just all curled up, just like no life in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I go up to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say, Vera, Vera.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
